{"tid":1305944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不譴責！九龍灣德福仔俾人打得好啊！香港人武力恆常化啦！","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:18:20.000Z","uid":70403,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"43c48d11800394f3d30a104dba9bcfa2ecb86881","tid":1305944,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再斟酌九龍灣仔應唔應該還手！<br />\n我地要多謝佢招和理非苦肉計就真！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">苦肉計用一次就好，用得多就冇效！</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">依單野分分鐘係會改變整場運動嘅打法<br />\n好有可能會喚醒和理非做勇武！<br />\n香港人開始相信要以武制暴！<br />\n<br />\n我地要大力宣傳！俾多啲人睇到！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 喚醒多啲人更加勇武<br />\n2. 廢老藍絲嘅暴力，無理<br />\n3. 警察執法嚴重不公</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我老母成日都話還手就係錯！<br />\n佢見到條片反而問點解唔還手？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為九龍灣仔咁樣挨打，警察放仼肥佬！<br />\n已經有好多和理非開始覺得自衛還手好正常！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係叫你主動打藍絲<br />\n係唔洗再怕自衛會失民心</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">參考下啲黑警點制服人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來唔會出拳！不過對方就好撚痛！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警權過大！藍絲暴力！<br />\n全民勇武！自衛無罪！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"36f0991ba451365b7fc9c225be3d1ad208e90528","tid":1305944,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97cd332044e16c8aae3c0ea35b18dbf77bc0c260","tid":1305944,"uid":70403,"like